snippet.title: Nibblers – Fruit Match Puzzle
snippet.description:
Get it here:  
http://rov.io/GetNibblersYT

From the creators of Angry Birds comes a delicious new matching game with super cute characters and tons of fresh and fruity puzzle gameplay. Meet the Nibblers, your fishy friends who only want to eat YUMMY fruit – ALL the yummy fruit! Om nom nom!

-----
Follow Nibblers: https://twitter.com/NibblersGame
Like Nibblers: https://www.facebook.com/NibblersOfficial
Follow Nibblers on Pinterest: https://www.pinterest.com/nibblersgame/
